lyrics:
[Verse]
I'm hungry, check the time, it's food o'clock
Got my appetite ready, stomach's on lock
I'm on a mission, searching for some flavors
Gonna satisfy this hunger, no time for haters

[Chorus]
Food, glorious food, ready to devour
Stepping up my game, I won't settle for sour
Bring on the feast, taste buds in a trance
Eating good, living life, taking every chance
